00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:21.440
line of monotherapies for solid or intractable cancer.

82
00:05:21.940 --> 00:05:25.600
But why this? The problem boils down to major

83
00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:29.340
structural liabilities. Number one, so you

84
00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:32.830
have 11 zinc-dependent HDAC paralogs that

85
00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:35.660
