00:07:33.712 --> 00:07:37.612
reporter assay in yeast. So what happens is that, as I told

119
00:07:37.652 --> 00:07:41.572
you, that this Sin3 Rpd3L complex is recruited

120
00:07:42.972 --> 00:07:46.772
