125
00:07:59.772 --> 00:08:03.332
So now we have a beautifully direct in cell functional readout,

126
00:08:03.772 --> 00:08:07.752
and using this approach, we screened 52,000 small molecules

127
00:08:07.792 --> 00:08:10.522
