01:40:30.336 --> 01:40:33.216
genomic alterations, those converged on the RAS pathway.

1672
01:40:33.936 --> 01:40:37.916
So this on-treatment resistance is clearly an emerging medical need, and

1673
01:40:38.036 --> 01:40:40.016
strategies to overcome this are required.

1674
01:40:40.676 --> 01:40:44.556
So one of the strategies that we have taken at RevMed is to come forward

1675
01:40:44.596 --> 01:40:47.686
with novel inhibitors that we believe will work in this setting of increased

1676
01:40:47.736 --> 01:40:51.176
oncogenic flux. To do so, we've built on the

1677
01:40:51.216 --> 01:40:54.476
hydrolysis-stimulating properties of deraxone rasip and

1678
01:40:54.976 --> 01:40:58.676
leveraging our sort of deep and really sophisticated understanding of the

1679
01:40:58.696 --> 01:41:02.485
